How We Engage
We have different models for client engagements for customised approach
01.
Dedicated Team
A team of talented engineers, with skills best suited to your business, is dedicated for you to manage. This allows for hiring cost reduction, expansion of existing projects and launching new products.
02.
Time & Material
Budget according to the amount of time spent and the number of engineers who worked on a project. If you have an agile approach towards project building, you’ve landed at the right place.
03.
Fixed Cost
We develop and deliver applications & services at a fixed price in accordance with initially agreed scope, specifications, deliverables, and deadlines. Since everything is preset, the chances of changes are very little.
04.
Partnership
We engage as thought partners with you and offer expert consultancy services. We deliver perfection in business analysis to help you draft an initial plan and product roadmap, and we don’t hesitate to go that extra mile for it.
Have a challenge you’d like to run by us? We are excited already.
